label: [babylonjs] 3d ticker wall
info:
### Description 

This is a 3D representation of a LED ticker.

### Result

![img](https://cdn.openmindmap.org/content/1698423949608_3d_ticker_5.gif)

### Requirements

This requirements the following Node-RED nodes:

- [node-red-contrib-web-babylonjs](https://flows.nodered.org/node/node-red-contrib-web-babylonjs)
- [introspection](https://flows.nodered.org/node/@gregoriusrippenstein/node-red-contrib-introspection) (optional)

### Using

Install the flow, got to `http://noded:1880/scene` (as described in [babylon](https://flows.nodered.org/node/node-red-contrib-web-babylonjs)), then hit one of the following keys:

- `a` to start text scrolling
- `s` to stop text scrolling
- `n` to reload the scene (good for development)
- `y` to reset paticles back to being flat
- `t` to give each particle a random height
